Options implemented:
-l: Long listing format
‐R: Recursive
‐a: all
-d: list directory entries instead of contents
‐S: sort by file size
‐t: sort by modification time

Note:
        Combinations allowed.
        Incase of Conflicting options, last one encountered on command line is given preference.
        Default sorting order is lexical.
        Using '-d' switches off '-R'
